re results than we imagined! There\u2019s good news somewhere every day, and encouraging trends across the world. People\u2019s attitudes are changing. People are better educated, healthier, live longer and have more access to clean water and resources than ever before. Social media continues to make a huge, positive difference in people\u2019s lives. Even the solidarity and willpower shown by protesters over Ferguson around the USA and around the world is encouraging!\nI\u2019m not giving you all this good news and encouraging you all to keep a positive attitude about the world to drown out the bad things and try to make you forget about Ferguson or Mexico or Hong Kong - far from it. I want you to remember them. Don\u2019t stop remembering them, don\u2019t stop signal boosting, don\u2019t let these issues die. But don\u2019t forget that the world can become a better place, and is becoming a better place for so many people in so many respects. I\u2019m not trying to uplift you and make your day better so you can put on a blindfold and forget about these important issues - I\u2019m trying to uplift you and make you feel better about the world so you\u2019ll have the spirit and determination to keep fighting and never lose hope for - and compassion for - humanity! In the words of Samwise Gamgee, \u201Cthere is some good in the world - and it\u2019s worth fighting for!\u201D\n","created_at":"Thu, 27 Nov 2014 08:29:37 +0000","id":"1e4760f85d6eae80860fa3c938627375","link":"http://i-want-a-callisto.tumblr.com/post/103710548336/procyonvulpecula-im-posting-a-lot-about","media_type":"text","received_at":1417076978.2605000,"schema":{"version":3},"subtype":"post","type":"tumblr","tags":["tab7"]},"language":{"tag":"en","tag_extended":"en","confidence":99},"tumblr":{"activity":"CreatePost","blog_name":"i-want-a-callisto","blogid":"102247317","body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://procyonvulpecula.tumblr.com/post/103709619386/im-posting-a-lot-about-ferguson-and-mexico-